            <div class="result-stat">99.9% complication-free</div>
          </div>

          <div class="result-card">
            <div class="result-icon">‚ú®</div>
            <h3>Thorough Cleaning</h3>
            <p>Unlike DIY attempts, professional removal gets everything out, leaving your ears completely clear.</p>
            <div class="result-stat">100% wax removal guaranteed</div>
          </div>

