              <div class="what-this-means">
                <strong>What this means for you:</strong> The choice isn't random - it's tailored to exactly what's happening in YOUR ears.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-icon">üß†</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>They Consider Your Comfort & Safety</h3>
              <p>Based on your medical history, current health, and personal preferences, they select the method that will be most comfortable and safest for you.</p>
              <div class="what-this-means">
                <strong>What this means for you:</strong> You don't have to worry about choosing something that might not be right for your situation.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div class="step-content">
