              <div class="patient-note">üí≠ "Finally someone who could see what was causing my problems!"</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="journey-step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Method Selection & Explanation (2 mins)</h3>
