              <div class="patient-note">üí≠ "Kept expecting it to be uncomfortable, but it never was."</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="journey-step">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Immediate Relief & Cleanup (5 mins)</h3>
