              <div class="patient-note">üí≠ "The relief was instant. Wish I'd done this months ago!"</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="appointment-reality">
          <h3>The Real Experience</h3>
          <p>Most people are amazed at how straightforward and comfortable the whole process is. The biggest surprise is usually how much wax comes out and how immediately your hearing improves. Total appointment time is typically 30-45 minutes, and most of that is talking, not treatment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

